title: Pete Tong Essential Selection 06/02/2009
description:
Pete Tong's Essential Selection Friday 6 February 2009

Pete's armed with all the super hot tunes! He chats to Paul Van Dyk & Eric Prydz on the phone and this week's Essential New Tune is a first play from Calvin Harris.

Broadcast: BBC Radio 1, International
